      "listener": null,
      "text": "晋城",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只问最近的是哪里？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_fen_yang",
      "speaker_name": "范汾阳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "最近的却是'汾记布庄'了，但那地方……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那地方有床么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_fen_yang",
      "speaker_name": "范汾阳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自然有的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有床就好。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那地方有酒么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_fen_yang",
      "speaker_name": "范汾阳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自然有的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有酒就好。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "汾记布庄",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_fen_yang",
      "speaker_name": "范汾阳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "越来越懒了……可恨。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_fen_yang",
      "speaker_name": "范汾阳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些奴才莫非死光了不成？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_fen_yang",
      "speaker_name": "范汾阳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这其中必有缘故……必有缘故……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他找谁？他就是这家店的老板，你不认得？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_fen_yang",
      "speaker_name": "范汾阳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张老板可知敝店发生了什么事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_chao_gui",
      "speaker_name": "张朝贵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下也正在奇怪，昨天半夜里，突然来了几辆大车，将贵号里的存货全搬空了，贵号伙计想必是赶着办货，所以……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "昨日半夜……半夜……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "汾记钱庄",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "汾记钱庄",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_shou_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "范守成",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道，只是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_shou_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "范守成",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "倒没有外人来拆咱们的台。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_fen_yang",
      "speaker_name": "范汾阳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既无外人，却又是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_shou_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "范守成",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来提银子的乃是七姑娘。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_fen_yang",
      "speaker_name": "范汾阳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位姑奶奶，当真害煞人了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她可是亲自来的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_shou_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "范守成",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她若不亲自来，我也没这么容易……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她一个人来的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她一个人搬得动？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_shou_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "范守成",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有银子，还愁雇不着马车？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_shou_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "范守成",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来你就是熊猫儿！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，我就是熊猫儿，你……你怎样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你自然想不到，我本来就没有大侠的模样。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你竟如此怕她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_shou_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "范守成",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_fen_yang",
      "speaker_name": "范汾阳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "信上写的是什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非信上有话骂我，你不便让我瞧。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咳……这……咳咳……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这封信除了骂你之外，还有更惊人的消息。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但词句倒也通顺，就和她说话似的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但事情哪有如此容易。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有什么不容易，咱们既已知道他行踪……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你我纵然已知他行踪，但王怜花下落不明，朱七七心意未测……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些事都可暂时放在一边的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_fen_yang",
      "speaker_name": "范汾阳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是，久闻'快活王'手下，非但四大使者武功惊人，随行三十六骑，亦无一弱者……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁说要逃了？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然不逃，咱们就到太行山去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我几时不答应你的事了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，就一言为定。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_fen_yang",
      "speaker_name": "范汾阳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小弟也……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "范兄还是不去的好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_fen_yang",
      "speaker_name": "范汾阳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小弟虽然胆小，却非畏事之徒……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_fen_yang",
      "speaker_name": "范汾阳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，小弟只得遵命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快活王",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "和你游山玩水虽不错，但……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你且随我来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我酒瘾虽发，眼睛可还是瞧得见的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知道，你且说来听听。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也不知道……我简直想也想不出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好汉子，好胆气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他一剑竟将这巨石砍成两半了么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快活王",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "纵有人说，你我也听不到的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你又想起酒了……喏喏，快看看那边一片突崖……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那里又有何故事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那里便是'太行三雁'的自尽之处。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那雪雁说了什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这又是为了什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来他少年时曾妄杀了一个人，而此人却待他义薄云天，他终身为此事歉疚难安，不知费了多少心血，将此人的后代，培养成人……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这雪雁也算得是有良心的了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "于是他便怎样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他竟约了那少年，到此与他见面。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "呀，原来如此，他兄弟可答应了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他可曾出手？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他兄弟呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那……那少年又如何？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……唉……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这故事莫非触及了你什么隐痛？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你可知道我也有个结义兄弟么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别人对他的结义兄弟，如此体谅，如此义气，那雪雁无论做出了什么，他兄弟都可体谅他的苦衷，而我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你难道会对不起你那结义弟兄？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你那结义弟兄只怕是女的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你怎会知道？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我早知什么事都瞒不过你，我本该当时就告诉你的，只是我……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自然有的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错！我的秘密本就比谁都多。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当今天下，可有人知道你的身世来历？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只怕……绝无仅有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有什么不同？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "多谢。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你瞧，这是什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们下去瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好轻功，我也来试试。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "砰",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎样了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "倒楣……这里居然会有鸡骨头。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "非但有鸡骨头，只怕还有别的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是酒杯的碎片。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但此人却用它在山野中喝酒，而且还摔破了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你瞧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就只这一只耳环的价值，已够普通人家一年生活之用……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 610,
      "line_end": 610
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这又是什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 618,
      "line_end": 618
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来这必定是他们宿营打桩时留下的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 620,
      "line_end": 620
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "纵是蒙古王侯所居，也不过如此了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 626,
      "line_end": 626
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但此人，露宿一夜，便要如此大费周章。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱七七果然未曾骗我，他果然已来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他想回去，也回不去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快活王",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 648,
      "line_end": 648
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？他撞见鬼不成？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 660
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是如此。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 670,
      "line_end": 670
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但这雪地上既不似被人扫过，在此等情况下，他们势必也不会是倒退回去的……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 672,
      "line_end": 672
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么这车辙马迹又怎会突然不见了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 676,
      "line_end": 676
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这种情况我曾遇过一次，是在墓外，那是他们踏着原来脚印退回去的……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "第二次可是在那山上？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 680,
      "line_end": 680
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，那是他突然走入地道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 682,
      "line_end": 682
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我正是已瞧出了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 694,
      "line_end": 694
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你瞧出的是什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 696,
      "line_end": 696
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老天爷，你说的这话可真教人难懂。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 702,
      "line_end": 702
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道你还瞧不出这雪地有什么特别之处？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 704,
      "line_end": 704
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你瞧这片雪地是否干净整齐得很？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 712,
      "line_end": 712
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯！太干净了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 714,
      "line_end": 714
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯……嗯，不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 720,
      "line_end": 720
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯！有道理……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 726,
      "line_end": 726
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你就该懂了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 728,
      "line_end": 728
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只因这片雪地本是人工铺上去的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 734,
      "line_end": 734
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人工铺上去的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 736,
      "line_end": 736
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好小子，居然肯花这么多力气。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 742,
      "line_end": 742
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "反正出力气的又不是他自己。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 744,
      "line_end": 744
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一天还未过去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 762,
      "line_end": 762
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但天已黑了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 764,
      "line_end": 764
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天黑了有何不好？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 766,
      "line_end": 766
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们白天都找不着线索，天黑了岂非……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 768,
      "line_end": 768
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "白天找不着，天黑了反有希望。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 770,
      "line_end": 770
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们莫非追错了方向？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 790,
      "line_end": 790
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他这盏灯是留给咱们的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 816,
      "line_end": 816
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "留给咱们的？莫非是诱人的陷阱？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 818,
      "line_end": 818
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这话我又不太懂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 824,
      "line_end": 824
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "像他这样的枭雄人物，决不会轻易低估对方的实力。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 826,
      "line_end": 826
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是此理。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 832,
      "line_end": 832
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "瞧他的行事，说不定早已在此山中遍布暗哨，说不定……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 838,
      "line_end": 838
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论怎样，待我先去瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 840,
      "line_end": 840
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此人行事，当真是人所难测。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 856,
      "line_end": 856
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但……这幅地图会不会是假的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 858,
      "line_end": 858
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但他并不怕咱们，又何必如此？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 866,
      "line_end": 866
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以此图也极有可能是真的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 868,
      "line_end": 868
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是如此。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 874,
      "line_end": 874
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "纵然想过，咱们也可当作根本未曾想过的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 904,
      "line_end": 904
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，这道理我总算想通了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 916,
      "line_end": 916
    }
  ],
